      "title": "Public assistance sought to identify 50 Temple Trees trespassers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): Police have sought public assistance in identifying 50 suspects who entered Temple Trees and caused property damage.",
        "The Police Media Division stated that the related investigations will be conducted by the Criminal Investigation Division of Colombo Crimes Division.",
        "Photographs of suspects have been released to the public as well.",
        "The police stated that members of the public can contact them via 0112421867, 0763477342 or the 1997 hotline, if they have information pertaining to the suspects."
      ],
